{"tid":291196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【世紀預言】89年《再見王老五》預示「終極劏房」成真","createTime":"2017-06-20T11:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T17:54:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aeefe7d24c1d030eb9d349d449ff0e8669c0d806","tid":291196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T11:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2016/12/07/9/9499ecbbc6d22ae611f8d4e5c3dc5d78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F9%2F9499ecbbc6d22ae611f8d4e5c3dc5d78.jpg&h=b3c1a3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SYjWRfqGhm0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSYjWRfqGhm0&d=3BopktSSyOhqtll0OlwmBAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=5b6aea68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SYjWRfqGhm0</a><br />\n早前有地產商推出史上最細的128呎屯門新盤，令全城嘩然，更被稱為「終極劏房」；發展商稱絕細單位是參考學生宿舍設計，又謂「皇帝都係瞓張床」令人啼笑皆非。<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：屯門菁雋開放式 最細128呎<br />\n<br />\n令人嘖嘖稱奇的是，早在1989年的電影《再見王老五》中，已預示了「終極劏房」的出現，片中地產經紀帶同鍾鎮濤與張曼玉睇樓，參觀的正是「終極劏房」超迷你單位。當中鍾鎮濤不斷投訴單位太細、放不下傢俱電器等，睡房更只能放下一張床！而片中地產經紀的詭辯亦是似曾相識：「市中心二千八蚊租去邊度搵丫」「擺唔到傢俬咪啱，擺唔到可以買少啲，買少啲可以慳多啲」「隱閉式餐檯，可以享受二人世界」「(因廁所太細，被質疑一開花灑馬桶便會濕透) 無人大便嘅時候開花灑架係咪？」<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：128呎單位設開放式廚房設備齊全<br />\n<br />\n電影橋段雖然好笑，但在30年後的今日，荒謬的電影情節成為了現實，相信很多人都笑不出來；更有網民表示：「最慘係，我覺得真係算接受到，如果宜家二千八，抵到爛」"},{"pid":"dc45d48b92ecebca106713596f7714ac4904f95b","tid":291196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T13:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a7a14df9fd14ccd19d34728dc3254d11388a93","tid":291196,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"冇咩人估到97後<br />\n共產黨繼續畀任炒樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641dc41087133835081289d3b53741fbe9f88676","tid":291196,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"如果市中心2千8蚊租真係接受到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51139600f38484dd66e774183f170642d377c27","tid":291196,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果市中心2千8蚊租真係接受到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n床位都租唔到😴"},{"pid":"6998113c5ed74916f1bc9e5bc50c2238a2518cb2","tid":291196,"uid":118771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果市中心2千8蚊租真係接受到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n環境差，經常性有蛇蟲鼠蟻都接受倒？"},{"pid":"0d8b023fae79b8b9965537dbf32e1912e93c544e","tid":291196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果市中心2千8蚊租真係接受到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n環境差，經常性有蛇蟲鼠蟻都接受倒？</blockquote><br />\n呢個單位好明顯係無呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1ee960cf58c0846244b41f4d646757c8644967","tid":291196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T13:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1520000/1524753/nano_hse_thumb_20161021_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1520000%2F1524753%2Fnano_hse_thumb_20161021_1024.jpg&h=faecc33f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92289c158aea5e8e1ee9ed5601608d9c9b5ef333","tid":291196,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"《終極監倉劏房》馬桶旁邊瞓梳化<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2hUCUPhVP4\" data-sr-url=\"htt